@startuml
title HireHub — Sequence Diagram\n(Job Application Lifecycle)

actor "Job Seeker" as Seeker
actor "Company" as Company
actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Browser" as UI
participant "Next.js\nServer" as Server
database "MongoDB" as DB

== 1. COMPANY REGISTRATION & APPROVAL ==

Company -> UI: Sign up
UI -> Server: signupCompany(form)
Server -> DB: User.create(role=COMPANY, status=PENDING_APPROVAL)
Server -> DB: CompanyProfile.create()
Server --> UI: redirect /login?message=pending-approval

Admin -> UI: Log in
UI -> Server: signIn(credentials)
Server -> DB: User.find(email)
Server --> UI: JWT token + redirect /admin/dashboard
Admin -> UI: Approve company
UI -> Server: approveCompany(companyId)
Server -> DB: User.update(status=ACTIVE)
Server -> DB: CompanyProfile.update(verified=true)
Server -> DB: Notification.create(type=COMPANY_APPROVED)
Server --> UI: ok

== 2. JOB POSTING ==

Company -> UI: Post new job
UI -> Server: createJob(formData)
Server -> DB: Job.create(status=ACTIVE)
Server -> DB: CompanyFollow.find(followers)
Server -> DB: Notification.create(type=NEW_JOB_POSTED)
Server --> UI: redirect /company/jobs

== 3. SEEKER APPLIES ==

Seeker -> UI: Browse feed
UI -> Server: GET /
Server -> DB: Job.find(ACTIVE)
Server -> DB: SeekerProfile.find()
Server -> DB: SavedJob.find()
Server -> DB: Application.find()
Server --> UI: scoredJobs + savedJobIds + appliedJobIds

Seeker -> UI: Click job → View details
UI -> Server: GET /jobs/[jobId]
Server -> DB: Job.findById()
Server -> DB: Application.findOne({jobId, seekerId})
Server --> UI: Job details + applicationStatus

Seeker -> UI: Click "Apply Now"
UI -> Server: applyToJob(jobId, formData)
Server -> DB: Application.create(status=PENDING)
Server --> UI: { ok: true }
UI -> UI: Show "Applied" badge

== 4. COMPANY REVIEWS ==

Company -> UI: View applicants
UI -> Server: GET /company/jobs/[jobId]/applicants
Server -> DB: Application.find({jobId})
Server -> DB: SeekerProfile.find() + matchScore()
Server --> UI: Applicants sorted by match score

Company -> UI: Approve applicant
UI -> Server: reviewApplicant(appId, formData)
Server -> DB: Application.update(status=APPROVED)
Server -> DB: Notification.create(type=APPLICATION_STATUS_CHANGED)
Server --> UI: { ok: true }

== 5. NOTIFICATION POLLING ==

UI -> Server: fetch /api/notifications (every 30s)
Server -> DB: Notification.find({userId, read:false})
Server --> UI: { count, notifications }

@enduml
